{"tid":1165516,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"意大利多個航空運輸員工工會發起罷工 影響多間航空公司","createTime":"2019-05-21T23:47:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T23:53:22.000Z","uid":205844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e0770e1c78bfb6db179f71255071f67df7836e74","tid":1165516,"uid":205844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T23:47:43.000Z","msg":"意大利多個代表航空運輸員工的工會，發起24小時罷工，令當地航空交通幾乎癱瘓。 數十名意大利航空公司的員工，手持橫額和旗幟，在羅馬的達文西機場外示威。 有工會代表說，罷工除了希望表達不滿過去六年公司因削減薪酬及裁員等所帶來的問題，亦希望提出航空業有改革的迫切需要。 受工潮影響，意大利航空超過300班國際及內陸航機取消。工會向受影響的乘客致歉。由於參與罷工的工會包括機師、機艙服務員及地勤，多間航空公司航班亦受影響。<br />\n<br />\n<ins><a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/world/5ce42ac0e603833e600032f4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fworld%2F5ce42ac0e603833e600032f4&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TT44BXU%2FO%2BPkTPvsbUsuc1I%3D&h=2e7065b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/world/5ce42ac0e603833e600032f4</a></ins>/<br />\n<br />\n港哩繼續返工不了，人地係道罷工爭取權益<br />\n香港個個做縮頭龜，冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fefd98cd5ea3648d784da64cafa87f6f9d8be7ae","tid":1165516,"uid":205844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T23:48:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76f129a882f915dfa00a0e425109a15d399acda3","tid":1165516,"uid":205844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T23:49:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f395448e4e3dfa72accbf3c90356dcfeef1badf","tid":1165516,"uid":205844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T23:51:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4a6226f5c7a8723eeda6f774d0416cb607fa46bf","tid":1165516,"uid":242917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T23:52:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1038b9332e1cdb0c430c5c309eb4a34c2dc1f599","tid":1165516,"uid":205844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a6226f5c7a8723eeda6f774d0416cb607fa46bf","tid":1165516,"uid":242917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-